{"tid":772004,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《賽勒姆》易多葛德柏格加盟TNT科幻美劇《末日列車》","createTime":"2018-08-08T11:57:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T07:32:09.000Z","uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"39b2d5427afbc8f4d3622f154b0f661819306762","tid":772004,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:57:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/08/195708_5f2f9e8b2cba403074aa55907703ac05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F08%2F195708_5f2f9e8b2cba403074aa55907703ac05.jpg&h=e763ab68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTNT 科幻美劇《末日列車》（Snowpiercer）宣布最新卡司，《賽勒姆》（Salem）男星易多葛德柏格（Iddo Goldberg）將以主要演員身分加盟演出工程師一角。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n《末日列車》美劇版改編自 2013 年韓國導演奉俊昊執導、《美國隊長》克里斯伊凡（Chris Evans）主演的同名電影。故事背景設定在氣溫驟降、世界變成冰凍大地的七年後，描述僅存人類乘坐在永恆運轉的列車中，受到差別待遇的倖存者將尋找社會正義，對抗不同階級的人們。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n易多葛德柏格將飾演工程師班奈特（Bennett），他看到整體大局但知道魔鬼就在細節裡。作為其中一位最初幫助設計這輛火車的工程師，他也是少數之一知道其最深的秘密。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n該劇節目統籌為《黑色孤兒》（Orphan Black）共同主創格雷姆曼森（Graeme Manson）。主演為《美麗境界》奧斯卡女配角得主珍妮佛康納莉（Jennifer Connelly）、音樂劇《漢密爾頓》男星戴維德迪格斯（Daveed Diggs）。其餘卡司包括《紐約哈哈哈》米琪桑茉（Mickey Sumner）、《副校長的逆襲》朴蘇珊（Susan Park）、《厲陰宅2》班傑明海格（Benjamin Haigh）以及《紅雀》莎夏弗羅洛瓦（Sasha Frolova）。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nTNT 尚未公布《末日列車》美劇版首播日期，Netflix 已購得美國境外首播權，屆時將與美同步播出。（deadline）"},{"pid":"4023142ebe05e522dcaedd61292b9e0515a7dcb4","tid":772004,"uid":49391,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T12:00:59.000Z","msg":"有無人睇過美隊果套?<br />\n有一幕冰左條友隻手之後打碎,覺得好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/08/195946_db8869bc0f73cb2563c4f974e6bf20b7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F08%2F195946_db8869bc0f73cb2563c4f974e6bf20b7.gif&h=13edb7d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/08/195955_f22ba97e5b656e2f92ad1dca484df3b8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F08%2F195955_f22ba97e5b656e2f92ad1dca484df3b8.gif&h=f04cc8ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e0b5787c341222ef98859b6a7a2394bf9ca1665","tid":772004,"uid":3873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T15:20:02.000Z","msg":"其實最尾個細路入火車頭係修理零件定本身佢就係零件？唔係太記得"},{"pid":"381b6e3d1d6a92d6f59334973684631bb6560679","tid":772004,"uid":54931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5e0b5787c341222ef98859b6a7a2394bf9ca1665","tid":772004,"uid":3873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T15:20:02.000Z","msg":"其實最尾個細路入火車頭係修理零件定本身佢就係零件？唔係太記得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T15:21:48.000Z","msg":"部永動機根本就有一part 係要擺個細路入去做零件<br />\n上一個細路死左就換下一個 好似係"},{"pid":"b39a63df609bce00f974fba606fc87df2016ccdc","tid":772004,"uid":87723,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T15:50:56.000Z","msg":"反對派領袖係同個車主係識，每次反抗都係為左減少人口<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f079b661dd7b610e0a9f8ede6f2994226ee22037","tid":772004,"uid":179935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:56:16.000Z","msg":"食曱甴榚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df30ed857abd3051a0e6750b267f4554fc6915c8","tid":772004,"uid":29496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b39a63df609bce00f974fba606fc87df2016ccdc","tid":772004,"uid":87723,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T15:50:56.000Z","msg":"反對派領袖係同個車主係識，每次反抗都係為左減少人口<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T20:32:19.000Z","msg":"好現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}